# Cloudflare Pages — server-side redirects.
# Reference: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/

# Root → language-detected landing.
# Vietnam visitors → /vi/, everyone else → /en/.
# 302 (Found) so language switcher choices aren't permanently cached;
# Google still treats this as the canonical entry path because the
# destinations themselves return 200 + canonical to /lang/.
/   /vi/  302  Country=VN
/   /en/  302

# SPA Fallback rewrites for localized routing on Cloudflare Pages
/vi/*  /vi/index.html  200
/en/*  /en/index.html  200
